= Campaign Status

This sidebar belongs to the bundled demo template. It gives a whiteboard version
of the common SDAAH-style dashboard: simple resources, support, card progress,
advisor trust, and room for more status sections.

Resources: [+ demo_resources +]

Volunteer support: [+ demo_support : qdemo_level +]

Advisor trust: [+ demo_advisor_trust : qdemo_level +]

Card progress: [+ demo_card_progress : qdemo_level +]

[? if demo_support > 0 : Volunteer support is active. ?]
[? if demo_conflict > 0 : Observation pressure is active. ?]
[? if demo_card_progress > 0 : The starter deck has changed project state. ?]
[? if demo_advisor_trust > 0 : The advisor lane has contributed trust. ?]

